    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/e916cc6e78164ed981c7c6a0b6bfee71.avif?t=1726593056\" width=580 height=160 /></span><br><br>Hellcome 是一款具有挑战性且令人兴奋的生存派对游戏，玩家必须在成群的僵尸和其他地狱生物中杀出一条血路才能生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fcb9d15ba557390533cc7797bf937766.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=580 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fcb9d15ba557390533cc7797bf937766.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fcb9d15ba557390533cc7797bf937766.mp4?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你将控制各种角色，每个角色都有自己独特的能力。 更多可玩的角色和敌人即将推出！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人合作模式：</h2>你可以与朋友组队，共同应对游戏的挑战。 共同努力完成目标，击败老板，并尽可能长久地生存。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/36b17f93394e282491ed37f90586621c.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/36b17f93394e282491ed37f90586621c.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/36b17f93394e282491ed37f90586621c.mp4?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >激烈且具有挑战性的游戏玩法：</h2>尽管有轻松愉快的视觉效果，但<strong>没有自动瞄准让事情变得更容易！</strong>你需要依靠自己的技能和反应来击倒敌人 僵尸群。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/1964395eb6d2b474180111a1ed29a4c1.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/1964395eb6d2b474180111a1ed29a4c1.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/1964395eb6d2b474180111a1ed29a4c1.mp4?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解锁新的能力和构建：</h2>尝试不同的组合，找到最适合您的组合。 有大量的能力可供选择，总有新的东西有待发现。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fd787012e95b5d2cfd3937d7aa91a9fa.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fd787012e95b5d2cfd3937d7aa91a9fa.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/fd787012e95b5d2cfd3937d7aa91a9fa.mp4?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Hellcome 是一款惊险刺激且富有挑战性的游戏，非常适合喜欢 Roguelite 游戏、弹幕射击游戏和合作多人游戏体验的玩家。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/f7e2618f1d55eef8352da73b6c1f6acf.poster.avif?t=1726593056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/f7e2618f1d55eef8352da73b6c1f6acf.webm?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/f7e2618f1d55eef8352da73b6c1f6acf.mp4?t=1726593056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2294550/extras/029139ff2548c27a1bfc84a8227769bd.avif?t=1726593056\" width=620 height=200 /></span>",
